 compared to both models and simulations to further explore the\nimplications on processes which shape and evolve BCGs/MMCGs over the past\n$\\sim$7 Gyr.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Sep 2013 20:00:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 May 2014 20:54:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
